data.description: If you are looking for a dream home with a stunning view easy to commute to NYC, look no further than this beautifully brick colonial home. This property offers a rare combination of location and privacy. You will have a front porch, spacious yard and deck which is perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxing after a long day. Inside, you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath and one half bath, a  kitchen, a sun room and a big basement. There are hardwood floors throughout the house. Plenty of storage with a full attic with pull down stairs. The whole house is sun-drenched with natural light. You will enjoy the convenience of living near ShopRite, Walmart and many more restaurants and shops. You will also be close to Franklin Mineral Museum, Franklin Pond, Borough Park and Playground. This is an amazing opportunity that you do not want to miss. Come see it today and make it yours.
